      "heading": "树上前缀和 vs 树上倍增",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "table",
          "rows": [
            "|  | 树上前缀和 | 树上倍增 |",
            "| <strong>能力边界</strong> | 只能处理<strong>可逆操作</strong>（如：求和、异或和） | 还能处理<strong>不可逆操作</strong>（如：求 Max/Min） |",
            "| <strong>时间复杂度（构建/查询）</strong> | $O(n), O(\\log n)$ | $O(n \\log n), O(\\log n)$ |",
            "| <strong>空间复杂度</strong> | $O(n)$ | $O(n \\log n)$ |",
            "| <strong>代码实现</strong> | <strong>极简</strong>（1 行公式） | <strong>繁琐</strong>（需要拼凑 $2^i$，边界情况多） |"
          ],
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "树上前缀和",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>核心思想</strong>：所有的和都定义为<strong>从根节点到当前节点的累加</strong>。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>何时用</strong>：查询树上<strong>某条路径的点权/边权之和</strong>。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>预处理</strong>：DFS 一遍，<code>sum[u] = sum[fa] + weight[u]</code>。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>查询公式</strong>：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "如果是<strong>点权</strong>路径和（包含 $u, v$ 本身）：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<code>ans = sum[u] + sum[v] - sum[lca] - sum[fa[lca]]</code>",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "如果是<strong>边权</strong>路径和：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<code>ans = sum[u] + sum[v] - 2 * sum[lca]</code>",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "树上差分",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>何时用</strong>：频繁把树上某条路径上的所有点/边加上一个值，最后问各个点/边的值）",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "相当于树上前缀和的逆运算。普通数组区间 $[L, R]$ 加 $1$，差分是 $D[L]+1, D[R+1]-1$。树上同理。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>操作（给</strong> $u$ <strong>到</strong> $v$ <strong>路径上全加上</strong> $val$<strong>）</strong>：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "如果是<strong>点权</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "diff[u] += val;\ndiff[v] += val;\ndiff[lca] -= val;\ndiff[fa[lca]] -= val;",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "如果是<strong>边权</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "diff[u] += val;\ndiff[v] += val;\ndiff[lca] -= 2 * val;",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>收尾（求出最终每个点的值）</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "所有修改结束后，跑一遍自底向上的 DFS 求前缀和（其实是<strong>后缀和</strong>），子树的 <code>diff</code> 之和就是当前节点的最终值。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void dfs_ans(int u, int fa) {\n    for (int v : g[u]) {\n        if (v == fa) continue;\n        dfs_ans(v, u);\n        diff[u] += diff[v]; // 累加子树\n    }\n}",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
